 theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeCheckboxComponentTokensProvider":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecheckboxcomponenttokensprovider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of checkbox"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for  ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"checkboxes","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckbox"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllCheckboxComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide all tokens to the users."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/d